# Synology NAS metadata
@eaDir/

# NOTE: helm/, oat/, sdk/, openagentic/ ARE tracked (synced from upstream for deployment)

# Docs — internal working notes; track only curated OSS docs.
# Git won't descend into an ignored directory, so we use the /docs/*
# pattern (ignore direct children) + per-path negations to re-include the
# curated OSS doc subtrees/files (enterprise-setup, launch, and the
# README-linked zero-telemetry + air-gapped-install pages).
/docs/*
!/docs/enterprise-setup/
!/docs/launch/
!/docs/zero-telemetry.md
!/docs/air-gapped-install.md

